      <talk_paragraph index="001" image="" itemindex="">
         <talk_answer link_index="quick_job1" mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>[Quick Specialization]</html>]]></talk_answer>
         <talk_question mid="3"><![CDATA[<html>$Specialization Helper Irine${action:Talk}<BR>Hello, <FONT color=#387206>{user_class} {user_nick}</FONT><FONT color=#382000> </FONT>.<BR>I'm Helper Irine, and I'm here to help warriors change their specialization.</html>]]></talk_question>
      </talk_paragraph>
      <talk_paragraph index="quick_job1" image="" itemindex="">
         <talk_answer link_index="quick_job2" mid="27"><![CDATA[<html>Yes, I want to specialize right now.</html>]]></talk_answer>
         <talk_answer link_index="non_quick" mid="28"><![CDATA[<html>No, I'll choose a specialization once I have more experience.</html>]]></talk_answer>
         <talk_question mid="21"><![CDATA[<html>$Specialization Helper Irine${action:Talk}<BR>In the Test Room, you can try out different specializations before choosing a <FONT color=#a82424>2nd specialization</FONT>, and you can also get help from a Specialization Helper to <FONT color=#086171>skip the experience and complete your specialization</FONT>, then return to town. Would you like to specialize and return to town right away?<BR>
 <BR>
</html>]]></talk_question>
      </talk_paragraph>
      <talk_paragraph index="quick_job2" image="" itemindex="">
         <talk_answer link_index="job_ui" mid="29"><![CDATA[<html>[Select a specialization]</html>]]></talk_answer>
         <talk_question mid="24"><![CDATA[<html>$Specialization Helper Irine${action:Talk}<BR>
Good! Then I'll help you specialize right away. Which job would you like?<BR>
 <BR>
<FONT color=#7e12d2>※ Select [Specialize] to end the story here. To see all specialization stories, be sure to play the [Specialization Trial].</FONT><BR>
 <BR>
</html>]]></talk_question>
      </talk_paragraph>
      <talk_paragraph index="non_quick" image="" itemindex="">
         <talk_question mid="26"><![CDATA[<html>$Specialization Helper Irine${action:Talk}<BR>It's also a great idea to take your time and get some experience before deciding!<BR>I'll wait for you here. Come talk to me whenever you need me.</html>]]></talk_question>
      </talk_paragraph>
      <talk_paragraph index="change" image="" itemindex="">
